M|Best|1. *|B2B cn can be slightly more formal; B2C often benefits from conversational transitions
M|Best|2. *|Repeating the same phrase gets noticed (and not in a good way)
M|Best|3. *|Trust your reader; every sentence doesn't need a transition
M|Best|4. *|Transitions at paragraph starts help skimmers navigate
M|Best|5. *|Read aloud; if it sounds forced, simplify
M|Best|6. *|Put the important word or phrase early in the transition
M|Best|tx|---
